{"title":"Hello World","date":"2019-10-24T06:30:13.827Z","link":"2019/10/24/hello-world","updated":"2019-10-24T06:30:13.827Z","content":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\">Quick Start<a href=\"2019/10/24/hello-world#Quick-Start\"></a></h2><h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\">Create a new post<a href=\"2019/10/24/hello-world#Create-a-new-post\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">\"My New Post\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\">Run server<a href=\"2019/10/24/hello-world#Run-server\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\">Generate static files<a href=\"2019/10/24/hello-world#Generate-static-files\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\">Deploy to remote sites<a href=\"2019/10/24/hello-world#Deploy-to-remote-sites\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Deployment</a></p>\n","prev":{"title":"Fastdfs doc","link":"2019/10/25/Fastdfs doc"},"next":{"title":"django踩坑","link":"2019/10/18/django踩坑"},"plink":"http://jccjd.top/2019/10/24/hello-world/","toc":[{"title":"Quick Start","id":"Quick-Start","index":"1","children":[{"title":"Create a new post","id":"Create-a-new-post","index":"1.1"},{"title":"Run server","id":"Run-server","index":"1.2"},{"title":"Generate static files","id":"Generate-static-files","index":"1.3"},{"title":"Deploy to remote sites","id":"Deploy-to-remote-sites","index":"1.4"}]}],"copyright":{"link":"<a href=\"http://jccjd.top/2019/10/24/hello-world/\" title=\"Hello World\">http://jccjd.top/2019/10/24/hello-world/</a>","license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名 (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}